overview: The Young Lions Cup tournament returns! 16 rookies converge on Emmaus with one goal in mind: to capture the Cup! In the kind of match that could only happen in Season 3, Mister ZERO, Icarus & Mike Quackenbush team together for a non-tournament trios bout to face Jorge "Skayde" Rivera and The Dark Breed!
title: Chikara: Young Lions Cup 2 (Night 1)
